Revision history for Complete-Riap

0.07    2015-11-29 (PERLANCAR)

	- Adjust to Complete::Common 0.21.

        - [Removed] For more consistent user experience, remove per-function
	  options ci/map_case/exp_im_path/dif_leaf, users are now encouraged to
	  set these behaviors globally via Complete::Common.


0.06    2015-09-09 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.05    2015-03-07 (PERLANCAR)

	- Default dig_leaf to 0 instead of Complete::OPT_DIG_LEAF to avoid
	  slowness and error-proneness.


0.04    2015-01-13 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add option: dig_leaf.


0.03    2015-01-13 (PERLANCAR)

        - Add option: riap_client.

        - [dist] Update prereq to a non-broken version of Complete::Path.


0.02    2014-12-25 (PERLANCAR)

	- Use Complete::Path, to avoid code duplication and gain feature
	  like case-insensitive matching, map case, and expand immediate
	  paths.

	- Follow convention of Complete 0.06.


0.01     2014-12-02 (PERLANCAR)

         - First release.
